          <h2 class='white-background-title'>Eleanor and Laurent</h2>
          <p class='white-background-paragraph'>Eleanor & Laurent is the newest addition directly west of  "The Sweetest Place in Town" and is currently open Wednesday-Sunday 9-8. As a homage to the Garneau’s who settled the area, these “Founders of the Feast” are currently sharing the experience of a Parisian café for take-away, a boulangerie, and patisserie. Our house-cured charcuterie has recently been launched and our main floor rotisserie is in its final stages of completion. 
            <br><br>Follow us on Instagram <a href='https://www.instagram.com/eleanor.laurent/?hl=en' target="_blank">@eleanorandlaurent</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-md-4 family-column'>
          <img src='/images/kaffa-logo.png' class='family-logo'>
          <h2 class='white-background-title'>Kaffa Coffee Company</h2>
          <p class='white-background-paragraph'>Kaffa Roaster and Studio Coffee Company are currently working towards their own opening. It is however showcasing freshly roasted specialty coffees for The Sugarbowl, Eleanor & Laurent, and a few lucky establishments that caught wind of our new project. Kaffa is anticipating providing the broader Edmonton Community with a daytime cafe as well as a locally-driven & inspired studio space for both day & evening. 
            <br><br>Follow us on Instagram <a href='https://www.instagram.com/kaffaroasterandstudio/?hl=en' target="_blank">@kaffaroasterandstudio</a> for the most up-to-date information on what we’re up to leading up to our official opening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-md-4 family-column'>
          <img src='/images/petiteIza-logo.png' class='family-logo'>
          <h2 class='white-background-title'>La Petite Iza</h2>
          <p class='white-background-paragraph'>La Petite Iza is a bistro located on Eleanor & Laurent's uppermost floor and is currently booking for intimate gatherings. Please visit here to book.  
            <br><br>Also, follow us on Instagram <a href='https://www.instagram.com/la_petite_iza/?hl=en' target="_blank">@la_petite_iza</a></p>
